manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: Features of TMY V68 mini projector [ Native 1080P resolution and Compatible with 4K video ]: V68 led projector uses a native 1080P Full HD LCD screen, which improves the projected image quality to 1920*1080 resolution. Moreover, we have adopted the technology that supports 4K video source, so that this movie projector can support 4K video at the maximum.[ Ultra-fast 5G WiFi Connection ]: The ultra-high-speed 5G WiFi connection allows screen mirroring faster and more smoothly.[ Equipped with Bluetooth 5.1 ]: Through the Bluetooth function, you can wirelessly connect with Bluetooth speakers, headphones, etc.[ 320ANSI lumens high brightness ]: This V68 4k projector has upgraded brightness to 320ANSI lumens.

Enjoy 1080P Brighter Display Compared with similar projectors on the market, the V68 small projector uses a real 1080P LCD screen, which makes the projected picture quality clearer, more vivid and more delicate. Moreover, you can even clearly see the hair of the characters in the picture. You could even call it a TV projector.

Super Fast 5G WiFi Connection This video projector uses the latest 5G WiFi technology, you can mirror your iPhone and Android devices with the 5G WiFi, so you can watch videos or play games smoother and more stable. Ultra-fast 5G WiFi makes no lagging while phone gaming and watching videos. *Note: 1. Due to HDCP(High-bandwidth Digital Content Protection) agreement, screen mirroring doesn't work(no image or sound) when you try to mirror the content from some streaming services (Amazon Prime Video, Netflix, Hulu, etc.). Please play these videos by inserting a TV Stick/Roku/Chromcast into the projector. You can also connect to a laptop/computer to play via HDMI Connection (HDMI Cable Included). 2. The phones adopt miracast protocol are compatible with WiFi projectors. But some Android devices don't support miracast ( such as Google/Moto/Sony), so these models cannot be screen mirrored via wifi. You need to prepare a Chrome-cast to screen mirror your phone.

Built-in Bluetooth 5.1 & Upgraded Powerful Speaker With built-in upgraded powerful speaker, you can enjoy a cinematic audio-visual experience without connecting external speakers. Also, you can connect Bluetooth speakers wirelessly to get more wonderful sound, you can even make home cinema with V68 home projector and external Bluetooth speakers.

Explore More Fun to Use It with Different Device Equipped with a variety of interfaces, the V68 phone projector is compatible with lots of electronic devices. You can explore more fun to use it with smartphone, TV stick, Roku stick, Chrome-cast, PC, DVD player, game player etc. And we look forward to your sharing with us how you use it.

Enjoy Your Life with the V68 Home Projector The V68 hd projector can be used for many purposes, whether it is in work or in life, it will become an indispensable item for you. At work, you can use it in meetings. At breaks, you can use it to exercise, play games, and watch movies. Indoors, you can watch a romantic movie with your lover in the bedroom, or watch cartoons and play games with kids. Outdoors, you can take it with you for a romantic camping night while camping, or you can watch an outdoor movie in the yard with your family. Without complicated settings, both the elderly and children can easily operate to enjoy the fun.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on August 29, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars The best mini projector I have seen
reviews.reviewText: I have used a projector just about every single night for the last 5 years wow outside on my deck.This is by far the best mini projector I have seen. Incredibly easy to use right out of the box You just plug it in and there you go. You're done.You have to choose what language you want to use with the opening screen and then it takes you to the input screen where you can set the projector up to your preferences such as size of the display I simply use the default which I believe is 16x9. You could also change the variables such as color volume and other personal preferences. On that same opening screen you can choose both your input source and output source. I did not use the USB media port at any time because it was just too much ever to take a fire stick out of my TV in the house and bring it outside but I'm sure it would work flawlessly as everything else did on this projector. I connected it to my HDMI portal my laptop as I do with my other projector every night and have done for the last 4 years on several different projectors that I own. Immediately when I chose a 4K program through YouTube the clarity and quality of this picture became evident. The picture was absolutely incredible and for demonstration I showed the fish and underwater scenes which are posted here. This picture quality is actually equal to My large format projector that I use most every night. I'm outside on my deck seven nights a week rain or shine hot or cold because I have a retractable awning and I like cold weather! It is incredibly bright and they mentioned 12,000 lumens I am not sure if that is accurate. I'm not sure but you would actually have to have a meter to judge and it's every bit as good as my larger more expensive projector. Honestly the picture quality is just about as good as my 4K television in the living room and that was surprising. I don't have an iPhone so I tried Miracast from my Samsung to the projector with ease. Of course I never read the owners manual for this because I've been doing this for several years with other projectors and of the controls are very similar.The machine is definitely solid and very well built which the quality of the build seem to be better than any mini projector I have. I didn't have any need to adjust the color or saturation of the picture because it was just fine straight out of the box but all those things can be adjusted in the settings.I did briefly use the DLNA function but only to test its compatibility with my laptop by streaming some music. It worked very well but in order to use it you must have Windows 10 or 11 a compatible laptop or device and a compatible modem that supports the DLNA protocol. I on a Hitron CODA DOCSIS 3.1 modem which is certified for use with Comcast Charter Spectrum Cox etc and can be found for under $100. My Xfinity cable box is DLNA capable but I just haven't gotten around to try that yet though I'm sure it will work just as well on this machine as it does on my other projector.. and the photos you will see the size comparison between my current full size projector with this projector sitting on top.Overall I don't think you could possibly find a better many projector for even twice the price. I have seven projectors in my home right now that I've used at one time or another and this is by far one of the best overall I've ever had. Small it's portable and convenient you can simply carry it anywhere you want to go in order to use it at a friend's house or at church or what have you. One of my favorite features though is it has an actual lens cap! The lens will be protected every time you put it away No need to worry which also means you won't have to clean the lens nearly as much as with other many projectors that don't have a lens cap and that's a definite plus for me.If you're having a hard time deciding which many projector to buy I promise you if you buy this many projector at this incredible price you will not be disappointed!

reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Incredible compact projector with an impressive visual experience
reviews.reviewText: If you are looking for an incredible, portable projector at a great price point, look no further; this projector's picture quality is outstanding. The images are sharp, and crisp, providing a great visual experience. The fan operates quietly, ensuring minimal distraction during quiet or dialogue-heavy scenes. The projector's sleek and modern design is aesthetically pleasing to the eye. It's solid and well-constructed giving me the confidence that it will last for some time. Another standout feature is the projector's advanced audio capabilities. The projector provides built-in speakers that produce great sounds and support external speaker connections physically or wirelessly. It offers a large range of features to enhance convenience, including a user-friendly remote control, the ease of navigating through menus and settings, and adjustable zoom and focus options, making it effortless to achieve the desired picture size and clarity.To summarize, this has exceptional picture quality, brightness, versatility, and audio capabilities, it truly stands out from the competition. It's an absolute must-have!
